videos.description: Jordan Clarkson battles Paul George to create space and knocks down a 3-pointer from the top of the arc for the Jazz.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Clarkson fends off PG to lace a 3) 2021/06/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clarkson fends off PG to lace a 3

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard comes up with the steal as he rips the ball away from Donovan Mitchell and races down the court to stuff down a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kawhi rips Mitchell for a fast-break dunk) 2021/06/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kawhi rips Mitchell for a fast-break dunk

videos.description: Paul George dribbles into trouble but makes a tough pass to a cutting Nicolas Batum for a thunderous slam in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (George sets up Batum to drop the hammer) 2021/06/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: George sets up Batum to drop the hammer

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard takes matters into his own hands as he makes his way to the basket and skies to vandalize the rim on a powerful throwdown.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kawhi rattles the rim with vicious slam) 2021/06/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kawhi rattles the rim with vicious slam

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell limps off the court to the tunnel with an apparent lower extremity injury in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell limps to the tunnel with an injury) 2021/06/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell limps to the tunnel with an injury

videos.description: Ivica Zubac comes up with an easy slam dunk in the lane as Paul George penetrates and finds him with a nice alley-oop pass.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (PG lobs to Zubac for the slam) 2021/06/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: PG lobs to Zubac for the slam

videos.description: Paul George tells Lisa Salters that the Clippers are dead set on their goals and minimizing distractions and explains how the group is refocused after their tough loss to the Jazz in Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Paul George: The Jazz lit a fire under us after Game 2) 2021/06/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paul George: The Jazz lit a fire under us after Game 2

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard puts up 34 points, 12 rebounds and 5 assists, and Paul George adds 31 points and 5 assists of his own as the Clippers dominate the Jazz to take Game 3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Kawhi, PG lead Clippers to crucial Game 3 win) 2021/6/12 ESHEET SOTFULL SC

videos.headline: Kawhi, PG lead Clippers to crucial Game 3 win
